'''Nubians''' were [[Human/Legends|Humans]] native to the planet [[Nubia/Legends|Nubia]]. [[T'chooka D'oon]] was an Nubian [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] who lived during the waning [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

